{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/about/layout,_N_T_/about/page,_N_T_/about"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/about/__PAGE__","/about","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"fr\" class=\"montserrat_2f6ba378-module__x6Ry1W__variable h-full\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/e8f2fbee2754df70-s.p.1dqa_6e_ad4sj.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"/images/logo/iba-logo-horiz.png\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"/images/logo/iba-logo.png\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/1fli-ooxui_ni.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/0iq1i69206cyl.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/27jktro2p5rq9.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/07u_h6i539_wj.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/3p9eevrhj-twl.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-30ssd7nw2f5xe.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/1z--s6j29dfmo.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/1hn7r3n4plx-e.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/3dpq9k6e41pe-.js\" async=\"\"></script><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://player.vimeo.com\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"/><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://i.vimeocdn.com\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"/><link rel=\"dns-prefetch\" href=\"https://f.vimeocdn.com\"/><meta name=\"theme-color\" content=\"#ffffff\"/><title>À propos | International Business Alliance</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Mission, vision et valeurs d’IBA : approvisionnement durable, partenariats de référence et gouvernance éthique au service de la construction.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.2vob68tjqpejf.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0cz1d0mv5g_q7.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"font-sans flex min-h-full flex-col antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"pointer-events-none fixed left-[-9999px] top-0 z-0 h-[200px] w-[356px] overflow-hidden opacity-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><header class=\"fixed top-0 z-50 w-full border-b border-iba-sky/10 bg-white transition-shadow duration-300 shadow-none\"><div class=\"relative mx-auto flex w-full max-w-[90rem] items-center transition-[padding] duration-300 py-1 sm:py-1 px-5 pr-3 sm:px-8 sm:pr-4 md:px-16 lg:px-20\"><div class=\"flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center justify-start\"><a class=\"flex shrink-0 items-center leading-none transition-opacity hover:opacity-90\" aria-label=\"International Business Alliance\" href=\"/\"><img alt=\"International Business Alliance\" width=\"1600\" height=\"380\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"xl:h-[6.25rem] h-20 w-auto max-w-[min(100vw,500px)] object-contain object-left sm:h-20 sm:max-w-[500px] md:h-24 lg:h-28\" style=\"color:transparent\" src=\"/images/logo/iba-logo-horiz.png\"/></a></div><nav class=\"hidden shrink-0 items-center gap-6 whitespace-nowrap md:flex lg:gap-10\" aria-label=\"Principal\"><a class=\"group relative text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-iba-sky transition-colors hover:text-iba-orange\" href=\"/\">Accueil<span class=\"absolute -bottom-2 left-0 h-[2px] w-0 bg-iba-orange transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:w-full\"></span></a><a class=\"group relative text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-iba-sky transition-colors hover:text-iba-orange\" href=\"/about\">À Propos<span class=\"absolute -bottom-2 left-0 h-[2px] w-0 bg-iba-orange transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:w-full\"></span></a><a class=\"group relative text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-iba-sky transition-colors hover:text-iba-orange\" href=\"/projects\">Projets<span class=\"absolute -bottom-2 left-0 h-[2px] w-0 bg-iba-orange transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:w-full\"></span></a><a class=\"group relative text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-iba-sky transition-colors hover:text-iba-orange\" href=\"/products\">Produits<span class=\"absolute -bottom-2 left-0 h-[2px] w-0 bg-iba-orange transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:w-full\"></span></a><a class=\"group relative text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-iba-sky transition-colors hover:text-iba-orange\" href=\"/quotation\">Devis<span class=\"absolute -bottom-2 left-0 h-[2px] w-0 bg-iba-orange transition-all duration-300 ease-out group-hover:w-full\"></span></a></nav><div class=\"flex min-w-0 flex-1 items-center justify-end gap-2 sm:gap-3\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"group relative z-50 inline-flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-iba-sky/5 text-iba-sky transition-colors hover:bg-iba-sky hover:text-white md:hidden\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Ouvrir le menu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button><a class=\"hidden shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-iba-orange px-5 py-2.5 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white transition-colors hover:bg-iba-orange/90 md:inline-flex\" href=\"/contact\">Nous Contacter</a></div></div></header><main class=\"flex min-h-[100dvh] md:min-h-screen flex-col bg-background selection:bg-iba-navy selection:text-white\"><section class=\"relative scroll-mt-20 bg-background pt-[calc(6rem+1.5rem)] pb-16 sm:pt-[calc(7rem+1.5rem)] md:pb-24 overflow-hidden\" aria-labelledby=\"about-page-heading\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-[0.03]\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(var(--iba-sky) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, var(--iba-sky) 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:40px 40px\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-[90rem] px-5 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-20\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"mb-6 flex items-center gap-4\"><span class=\"h-px w-12 bg-iba-orange\"></span><p class=\"font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-iba-navy\">International Business Alliance</p></div><h1 id=\"about-page-heading\" class=\"mt-3 text-5xl font-black uppercase leading-[0.95] tracking-tighter text-iba-sky sm:text-6xl md:text-8xl\">À propos</h1><p class=\"mt-8 max-w-2xl text-lg font-medium leading-relaxed text-iba-muted md:text-xl border-l-2 border-iba-orange pl-6\">International Business Alliance — matériaux, partenariats et standards au service de la construction durable.</p></div></div><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-px left-0 z-20 w-full select-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1440 120\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"block w-full rotate-180\"><path d=\"M0 0H1440V75Q720 -5 0 75V0Z\" class=\"fill-iba-navy\"></path></svg></div></section><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-iba-navy py-20 text-white md:py-28 lg:py-32\"><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute -right-32 top-0 h-[600px] w-[600px] rounded-full bg-white/[0.04] blur-[100px]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute -left-32 bottom-0 h-[400px] w-[400px] rounded-full bg-iba-sky/[0.04] blur-[100px]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-[90rem] px-5 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-20\"><div class=\"relative mb-10 md:mb-14 lg:mb-16\"><div class=\"absolute -left-4 -top-10 -z-10 select-none text-[8rem] font-black leading-none sm:-top-12 sm:text-[10rem] md:text-[12rem] text-white/[0.06]\" aria-hidden=\"true\">01</div><div class=\"flex max-w-3xl flex-col gap-4 md:gap-5\"><span class=\"inline-flex w-fit items-center rounded-full border px-5 py-2 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] backdrop-blur-sm border-white/25 bg-white/10 text-white\">Notre mission</span><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-2 h-[2px] w-8 shrink-0 bg-iba-orange\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><p class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/70\">01 — Notre mission</p></div><h2 class=\"text-balance text-3xl font-extrabold uppercase leading-[1.08] tracking-tight md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-white\">Approvisionner, soutenir et<!-- --> <span class=\"text-iba-sky italic\">construire durablement.</span></h2><p class=\"max-w-2xl text-base font-medium leading-relaxed md:text-lg text-white/80\">Mettre à disposition des professionnels et des particuliers des matériaux de qualité pour garantir la réussite de leurs projets de construction. Nous nous engageons à offrir des solutions adaptées, un service efficace et un accompagnement de proximité pour chaque chantier.</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-12 grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-16 lg:items-start\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-8 space-y-6 text-base font-medium leading-relaxed text-white/90 md:text-lg\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white md:text-3xl border-b border-white/10 pb-4\">Une force qui bâtit l’avenir</h3><p class=\"text-xl font-light text-white/95\">Nous sommes la force qui bâtit l’avenir — une confiance qui s’inscrit dans la durée et à l’échelle mondiale.</p><p class=\"text-white/80\">Nous ne nous contentons pas de fournir des matériaux. Nous accompagnons nos partenaires et nos clients dans la réalisation de projets fiables et durables, en favorisant la transparence, la sécurité et la qualité.</p></div><aside class=\"group relative lg:col-span-4 overflow-hidden rounded-sm bg-iba-sky p-8 shadow-2xl lg:sticky lg:top-32 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 h-1.5 w-full bg-iba-orange transition-all duration-500 group-hover:bg-white\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-down-right mb-6 h-8 w-8 text-iba-navy opacity-50\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m7 7 10 10\"></path><path d=\"M17 7v10H7\"></path></svg><p class=\"font-mono text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-iba-navy\">Portée internationale</p><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm font-medium leading-relaxed text-white/85 md:text-base\">IBA collabore avec des partenaires et fournisseurs étrangers et locaux, et respecte des standards internationaux, ce qui lui permet de s’inscrire dans une dynamique d’ouverture sur le marché international des matériaux de construction.</p></div></aside></div></div><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-px left-0 z-20 w-full select-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1440 120\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"block w-full rotate-180 h-16 md:h-24\"><path d=\"M0 0H1440V75Q720 -5 0 75V0Z\" class=\"fill-background\"></path></svg></div></section><section class=\"relative overflow-x-hidden border-b border-iba-sky/10 bg-background py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-28\" aria-label=\"Vidéo de présentation\"><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-[0.04]\" style=\"background-image:radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, var(--iba-sky) 1px, transparent 2px);background-size:40px 40px\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 mx-auto aspect-video  max-w-full min-w-0 overflow-hidden bg-white border border-iba-sky/15 shadow-[0_24px_60px_-24px_rgba(40,37,97,0.25)]\"></div></section><section class=\"relative bg-background py-20 md:py-32\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-[90rem] px-5 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-20 text-center flex flex-col items-center\"><span class=\"mb-6 inline-block font-mono text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-iba-navy\">Notre vision<!-- --> // <!-- -->02 — Notre vision</span><h2 class=\"text-balance text-4xl font-black uppercase leading-[1.05] tracking-tighter text-iba-sky md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl max-w-5xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Être un partenaire de<!-- --> <span class=\"relative inline-block text-iba-navy\">référence dans la construction.<svg class=\"absolute -bottom-2 left-0 w-full h-3 text-iba-navy/30\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M0,50 L100,50\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"6\"></path></svg></span></h2><p class=\"mt-8 max-w-3xl text-lg font-medium leading-relaxed text-iba-muted md:text-xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Un avenir où chaque projet, petit ou grand, repose sur des matériaux solides et un approvisionnement fiable. Nous aspirons à devenir un acteur clé du secteur en contribuant activement au développement urbain et à la modernisation des infrastructures.</p></div><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-px left-0 z-20 w-full select-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1440 120\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"block w-full rotate-180\"><path d=\"M0 0H1440V75Q720 -5 0 75V0Z\" class=\"fill-iba-navy\"></path></svg></div></section><section class=\"relative overflow-x-clip bg-iba-navy py-20 text-white md:py-28 lg:py-32\"><div class=\"relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-[90rem] px-5 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-20\"><div class=\"relative mb-10 md:mb-14 lg:mb-16\"><div class=\"absolute -left-4 -top-10 -z-10 select-none text-[8rem] font-black leading-none sm:-top-12 sm:text-[10rem] md:text-[12rem] text-white/[0.06]\" aria-hidden=\"true\">03</div><div class=\"flex max-w-3xl flex-col gap-4 md:gap-5\"><span class=\"inline-flex w-fit items-center rounded-full border px-5 py-2 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] backdrop-blur-sm border-white/25 bg-white/10 text-white\">Notre impact</span><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-2 h-[2px] w-8 shrink-0 bg-iba-orange\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><p class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/70\">03 — Axes d’action</p></div><h2 class=\"text-balance text-3xl font-extrabold uppercase leading-[1.08] tracking-tight md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-white\">Agir avec<!-- --> <span class=\"text-iba-sky\">exigence et mesure</span></h2><p class=\"max-w-2xl text-base font-medium leading-relaxed md:text-lg text-white/80\">Trois leviers complémentaires pour ancrer notre mission dans des résultats concrets sur le terrain.</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-12 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-3\"><article class=\"group relative flex min-h-[16rem] flex-col bg-white/5 p-8 transition-all hover:bg-white/10\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute left-0 top-0 h-full w-1.5 bg-iba-orange transition-all duration-500 group-hover:w-2 group-hover:bg-white\"></div><span class=\"mb-4 font-mono text-4xl font-black text-white/10 transition-colors group-hover:text-white/20\">0<!-- -->1</span><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white md:text-2xl\">Impact ciblé</h3><p class=\"mt-4 flex-1 text-sm font-medium leading-relaxed text-white/80 md:text-base\">IBA vise à améliorer durablement le secteur de la construction en fournissant des matériaux de qualité, en contribuant au développement des infrastructures et en participant à la croissance économique locale et régionale.</p></article><article class=\"group relative flex min-h-[16rem] flex-col bg-white/5 p-8 transition-all hover:bg-white/10\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute left-0 top-0 h-full w-1.5 bg-iba-orange transition-all duration-500 group-hover:w-2 group-hover:bg-white\"></div><span class=\"mb-4 font-mono text-4xl font-black text-white/10 transition-colors group-hover:text-white/20\">0<!-- -->2</span><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white md:text-2xl\">Nos projets</h3><p class=\"mt-4 flex-1 text-sm font-medium leading-relaxed text-white/80 md:text-base\">Une trajectoire de chantiers et de partenariats qui illustrent notre capacité à livrer, à respecter les normes et à tenir nos engagements opérationnels.</p><a class=\"mt-8 inline-flex w-fit items-center border-b border-transparent pb-1 font-mono text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-iba-sky transition-all hover:border-white hover:text-white\" href=\"/projects\">Explorer<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right ml-2 h-3.5 w-3.5 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></article><article class=\"group relative flex min-h-[16rem] flex-col bg-white/5 p-8 transition-all hover:bg-white/10\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute left-0 top-0 h-full w-1.5 bg-iba-orange transition-all duration-500 group-hover:w-2 group-hover:bg-white\"></div><span class=\"mb-4 font-mono text-4xl font-black text-white/10 transition-colors group-hover:text-white/20\">0<!-- -->3</span><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-white md:text-2xl\">Gouvernance éthique</h3><p class=\"mt-4 flex-1 text-sm font-medium leading-relaxed text-white/80 md:text-base\">IBA adopte une gestion transparente et responsable, fondée sur l’intégrité, le respect des normes, la conformité légale et l’engagement envers ses partenaires, employés et clients.</p></article></div></div><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-px left-0 z-20 w-full select-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1440 120\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" class=\"block w-full rotate-180 h-16 md:h-24\"><path d=\"M0 0H1440V75Q720 -5 0 75V0Z\" class=\"fill-background\"></path></svg></div></section><section class=\"relative bg-background pt-16 pb-24 md:pt-32 lg:pb-40 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none flex justify-center opacity-60\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0\" style=\"background-image:linear-gradient(var(--iba-sky) 1px, transparent 1px), \n              linear-gradient(90deg, var(--iba-sky) 1px, transparent 1px);background-size:120px 120px;opacity:0.03\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0\" style=\"background-image:radial-gradient(circle at 0 0, var(--iba-sky) 2px, transparent 3px);background-size:120px 120px;opacity:0.08\"></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-[90rem] px-5 sm:px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-20\"><div class=\"relative lg:mb-16 mb-12 md:mb-16\"><div class=\"absolute -left-4 -top-10 -z-10 select-none text-[8rem] font-black leading-none sm:-top-12 sm:text-[10rem] md:text-[12rem] text-iba-sky/[0.05]\" aria-hidden=\"true\">04</div><div class=\"flex max-w-3xl flex-col gap-4 md:gap-5\"><span class=\"inline-flex w-fit items-center rounded-full border px-5 py-2 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] backdrop-blur-sm border-iba-sky/15 bg-iba-sky/[0.04] text-iba-sky\">Notre charte</span><div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"mt-2 h-[2px] w-8 shrink-0 bg-iba-orange\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><p class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-iba-sky/55\">04 — Valeurs &amp; principes</p></div><h2 class=\"text-balance text-3xl font-extrabold uppercase leading-[1.08] tracking-tight md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-iba-sky\">Notre<!-- --> <span class=\"text-iba-navy\">philosophie</span></h2><p class=\"max-w-2xl text-base font-medium leading-relaxed md:text-lg text-iba-muted\">Chez IBA, nous croyons que le développement du secteur de la construction repose sur une gestion responsable, des partenariats solides et une vision durable. Notre approche valorise le savoir-faire local tout en s’alignant sur les standards internationaux.</p></div></div><div class=\"grid auto-rows-[180px] grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 md:gap-6 mt-16\" style=\"opacity:0\"><div class=\"group relative flex flex-col justify-between border border-iba-sky/20 bg-white p-6 md:p-8 transition-colors duration-300 hover:bg-iba-sky md:col-span-2\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px) scale(0.98)\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-3 h-3 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-iba-sky transition-colors group-hover:border-iba-navy\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-3 h-3 border-t-2 border-r-2 border-iba-sky transition-colors group-hover:border-iba-navy\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-3 h-3 border-b-2 border-l-2 border-iba-sky transition-colors group-hover:border-iba-navy\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-3 h-3 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-iba-sky transition-colors group-hover:border-iba-navy\"></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"font-mono text-xs font-bold text-iba-sky/40 transition-colors group-hover:text-iba-navy\">ID_0<!-- -->1</span><span class=\"text-iba-sky/20 transition-colors group-hover:text-iba-navy/50 text-[10px]\">⬢</span></div><h3 class=\"font-sans text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-iba-sky transition-colors group-hover:text-white\">Intégrité et transparence</h3><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 h-1 w-0 bg-iba-orange transition-all duration-500 ease-out group-hover:w-full\"></div></div><div class=\"group relative flex flex-col justify-between border border-iba-sky/20 bg-white p-6 md:p-8 transiti